For all the challenges, use namespaces.

XML Parser
==========
* create the code that will parse the contents of sample.xml
* the script should output the unique list of tags used in the xml file
* the script should output all text content as a flat string

SimpleXML
=========
* create a script that will parse the contents of sample.xml and echo out the tags and text content in the following format:
    tagName::content
* instantiate SimpleXML using a string instead of a file
* echo the entire XML string
* add a new movie "Batman"
* save the file

